arStrings.szText: Your damage over time effects are increased by {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|1%x|]{/c} for each different Crowd Control effect on the target. {c_important}{u}Unstoppable{/u}{/c} monsters and {c_important}Staggered{/c} bosses instead take {c_random}[Affix_Value_2|%x|]{/c} increased damage from your damage over time effects.
